:03:57.000Z","msg":"巴打做緊邊行嘅marketing?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"F&amp;B 傻閪先做呢個field （即係我）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"做F&amp;B有咩辛酸史<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:51:16.000Z","msg":"F&amp;B 除左食同飲你可以當福利，人工低，辛苦（無疫情下係勁多活動要跟，吃力不討好。）跟retail客就串過馬撚，跟catering buyer 串過馬撚，廚就on99唔企理無black &amp; white 留底。<br />\n<br />\n總之一句講晒F&amp;B離不開瘋狂湊仔"},{"pid":"a1a78debe02caa617462fba3a00e44d626ea8d67","tid":2368963,"uid":211878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33286d1a9909f3150c599517ee030789b52297ad","tid":2368963,"uid":194481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"236c002e9fb56ef3f1f751fb03312cce0eb40012","tid":2368963,"uid":211878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4ec007926b3bc0dc97c702def343b85882bd11c","tid":2368963,"uid":194481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"本身都跟開FMCG industry嘅大brand，但真係無乜興趣 想轉下啲場地嘅marketing...通常Marketing executive係咪都好少請行外人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔難 始終MA/ME都係entry level<br />\n可以吹返啲transferable skills<br />\n做下research俾佢知道你對個行業都有了解同熱誠<br />\n同埋都睇你本身間Agency出唔出名<br />\n<br />\nBtw FMCG夠闊 我覺得會相對易搵到出路啲<br />\n不過無興趣就無計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"FMCG人工應該再好啲...但做咗一年覺得有興趣嘅工真係好重要 ot都唔會覺得攞你命咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"係 FMCG多大brands揀 又好搵錢<br />\n你想做嘅場地marketing <br />\n係咪coworking space, event租場 Atlaspace, The Wave嗰類?<br />\n<br />\n有興趣先好做 絕對啱啊<br />\n始終marketing辛苦得嚟 付出同收入唔成正比<br />\n又要keep up to the trends <br />\n我都係慣性OT狗 <br />\n但起碼鍾意做同知自己行緊去邊 <br />\n先keep到團火頂硬上"},{"pid":"f57ddb7096fcd886878754f55400da1ec31d0fd5","tid":2368963,"uid":194481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1a78debe02caa617462fba3a00e44d6