2130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcced16a0f72c758f31a5a419d0d0281f5a3dd8","tid":2368963,"uid":192573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f79ec8c49b5f97029288798ca8168950c149bbff","tid":2368963,"uid":182130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"真係唔好，我media agency 7年經驗都要走，呢一行同我2011first grad 入行果陣比已經係明顯downtrend哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"但有media知識/execution experience會搶手啲，想請問巴打如果下份入inhouse，呢方面經驗可以點累積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"雖然有做過campaign 好似會易啲入in house，但其實啲exp基本上係無用，純粹係用黎當入場券，咁倒不如fresh grad 直接去做in house，如果入到的話...<br />\n<br />\nIn house都要睇你做邊一行，你agency有做過相關行業既客或者有少少幫助，如果無，其實同白紙無分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"原本fg後入agency都係為左以後marketing工任揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家做左3年agency, 搵in house真係冇乜聲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至連轉行都考慮埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601b75a80a787982d301221bf38ae0263808bf44","tid":2368963,"uid":119907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a8ec19a26479a86eb192f1df9e75016f44ac28e","tid":2368963,"uid":211878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b085841501c3b7d7b0c1ccf4128bdc09282fb84","tid":2368963,"uid":132941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afcd298a743435dcdcd181db85c6a89d4c376c48","tid":2368963,"uid":211878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"工作量大係真 <br />\n間中會因為turnover rate高而唔夠人手/接手其他人啲嘢 搞到會忙上加忙<br />\nCareer path一定唔夠ib, audit穩定<br />\n起薪低 升幅, 頂點就好睇做邊瓣嘅marketing<br />\n<br />\n答返樓主 一係一開始就做in-house MA<br />\n一係做到Account manager先轉in-house<br />\n要做幾多年就睇你斤兩<br />\n易唔易搵就睇你之前agency湊咩客、想做咩industry<br />\n<br />\n奉勸無興趣、唔覺得呢行好玩就唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"點解仲會有人入行，萬令兩萬蚊但做到凌晨，星期六日都要覆客，前途又一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"門檻低 同好玩啩<br />\nOT同放假覆客唔係必然嘅 睇公司文化同客<br />\n前途嘅嘢 人各有志啫<br />\n同埋都係嗰句 marketing要睇做邊瓣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"Agency門檻低...我見左10+份agency得一份出offer比我（仲要係伏嘅，仲有一份叫我做freelance)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：實習同grade左之後都係做大公司"},{"pid":"97b73ef805fd7dab60c95bc29082e1a2bca980e3","tid":2368963,"uid":194481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"792407f493ac5f8a7a64b1af4da1c62256c09591","tid":2368963,"uid":192573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55b243b52f7757373d94cfb2e0a7e64f4778398c","tid":2368963,"uid":182130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcced16a0f72c758f31a5a419d0d0281f5a3dd8","tid":2368963,"uid":192573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"但有media知識/execution experience會搶手啲，想請問巴打如果下份入inhouse，呢方面經驗可以點累積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"雖然有做過campaign 好似會易啲入in house，但其實啲exp基本上係無用，純粹係用黎當入場券，咁倒不如fresh grad 直接去做in house，如果入到的話...<br />\n<br />\nIn house都要睇你做邊一行，你agency有做過相關行業既客或者有少少幫助，如果無，其實同白紙無分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"原本fg後入agency都係為左以後marketing工任揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家做左3年agency, 搵in house真係冇乜聲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至連轉行都考慮埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:45:01.000Z","msg":"巴打搵緊邊個field嘅in house?"},{"pid":"4780adaf57b1039e9d701b7c9e13b815745eec84","tid":2368963,"uid":192573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97b73ef805fd7dab60c95bc29082e1a2bca980e3","tid":2368963,"uid":194481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"792407f493ac5f8a7a64b1af4da1c62256c09591","tid":2368963,"uid":192573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55b243b52f7757373d94cfb2e0a7e64f4778398c","tid":2368963,"uid":182130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"雖然有做過campaign 好似會易啲入in house，但其實啲exp基本上係無用，純粹係用黎當入場券，咁倒不如fresh grad 直接去做in house，如果入到的話...<br />\n<br />\nIn house都要睇你做邊一行，你agency有做過相關行業既客或者有少少幫助，如果無，其實同白紙無分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"原本fg後入agency都係為左以後marketing工任揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家做左3年agency, 搵in house真係冇乜聲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至連轉行都考慮埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:45:01.000Z","msg":"巴打搵緊邊個field嘅in house?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"FMCG<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好玩啲<br />\n主力搵digital marketing"},{"pid":"e3a01d7f76379da16b634545d99938d786148b9f","tid":2368963,"uid":33203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"如果你未畢業，奉勸你唔好做mkt。呢行起薪低，講緊fg得11、12k。工時長，agency chur就一定，in-house就睇你彩數。<br />\n<br />\n我而家做緊嗰間所謂過百億市值上市公司in-house digital，run到好似startup咁癲，日日7/24，試過星期六出咗街都俾上司叫你報數。<br />\n<br />\n開頭嗰1、2年你都仲可能未覺太差，但之後你會發現同身邊朋友差距越嚟越大。人哋搵緊3萬幾4萬，你先得2萬中，仲日日最少做10個鐘做到懷疑人生，去到差唔多成家立室嘅時候，仲大壓力。我而家洗濕咗個頭，做咗成7年，抽唔到身。 <br />\n<br />\n如果你一定要試做mkt，咁最好係做digital，始終market demand大，喺呢行叫有前景啲。<br />\n<br />\n最後一句：做marketing賤過狗"},{"pid":"d83629b415f80a31029b47e7183d2222d4207b93","tid":2368963,"uid":213384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"308fc37bf6a25dc35f43af3c200d8aa60fcd0424","tid":2368963,"uid":194481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"多數係agency做幾多年先轉去做in house marketing比較好？<br />\n本身讀communication出身，做完agency再做marketing易唔易搵工？<br />\n求經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"小弟第一份工就係agency, 一做就十四年<br />\n<br />\nagency其實都有分好多種, 好難就咁同in house比<br />\n<br />\n傳統creative agency 主要分creative同account services, 做as頭幾年真係頭跟尾, 完全唔知JM9。最慘係傳統creative agency都愈做愈頹...真係唔好試<br />\n<br />\nmedia agency就真係辛苦既, 但就可以短時間學到好多hands on既野。但都要小心, 如果派入左條team, 係跟傳統媒體好似電影或者報紙, 咁就唔做好過做。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多local agency, 好處係冇咁怕, 同可以會接觸到多d唔同既野, 由paid media到website, crm, GA, socail....等等, 但唔好處就係做事冇大agency咁咁有規劃。<br />\n<br />\n小結<br />\n大agency做事有framwork, 如果做你唔死, 可以學到好多presentation同做powerpoint 開會既softskill, 呢d係local agency同in house都唔會比到你既野。<br />\ninhouse 就會有多d自己生活, 亦都會知道多d 同生意直接有關既事同數字, 呢d agency未必知。不過要小心揀行業...因為入左某一行既in house, 要轉工好多時都會限制左係果一行, 開錯左個頭就慘。"}]}